<pb n="0758a" ed="T" id="T14.0494.0758a"/>
<lb n="0758a01" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/><head type="no">No. 494</head>
<lb n="0758a02" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><note n="0758001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（佛說）＋阿【明】</note><app n="0758001"><lem wit="【大】">阿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">佛說阿</rdg></app>難七夢經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0758a03" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator">東晉<note n="0758002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">天竺三藏＝西域沙門【三】【宮】</note><note n="0758002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">天竺三藏＝西域沙門【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0758002"><lem wit="【大】">天竺三藏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">西域沙門</rdg></app>竺曇無蘭譯</byline>
<lb n="0758a04" ed="T"/><div1 type="jing"><p id="pT14p0758a0401">阿難在舍衛國，有七種夢，來問於佛：一者、
<lb n="0758a05" ed="T"/><note n="0758003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（夢）＋陂【三】【宮】</note><note n="0758003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（夢）＋陂【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0758003"><lem wit="【大】">陂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">夢陂</rdg></app>池火炎滔天；二者、夢日月沒，星宿亦沒；三
<lb n="0758a06" ed="T"/>者、夢出家比丘轉在於不淨坑塹之中，在家
<lb n="0758a07" ed="T"/>白衣登頭而出；四者、夢群&CB00337;來觝<note n="0758004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00247;＝突【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0758004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00247;＝突【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0758004"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00247;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">突</rdg></app>栴檀
<lb n="0758a08" ed="T"/>林<note n="0758005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔怪之〕－【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0758005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔怪之〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0758005"><lem wit="【大】">怪之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>；五者、夢頭戴須彌山，不以為重；六
<lb n="0758a09" ed="T"/>者、夢大象棄小象；七者、夢師子王名華<note n="0758006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">撒＝薩【三】【宮】</note><note n="0758006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">撒＝薩【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0758006"><lem wit="【大】">撒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">薩</rdg></app>，頭
<lb n="0758a10" ed="T"/>上有七毫毛，在地而死，一切禽獸，見故怖
<lb n="0758a11" ed="T"/>畏，後見身中蟲出，然後食之。以此惡夢，來
<lb n="0758a12" ed="T"/>問於佛。</p><p id="pT14p0758a1204" place="inline">佛時在舍衛國普會講堂上，與波斯
<lb n="0758a13" ed="T"/>匿王說法：苦、<note n="0758007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">習＝集【三】【宮】</note><note n="0758007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">習＝集【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0758007"><lem wit="【大】">習</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">集</rdg></app>、滅、得道為樂。見阿難憂色
<lb n="0758a14" ed="T"/>愁苦叵言。佛告阿難：「汝於夢者，皆為當來
<lb n="0758a15" ed="T"/>五濁惡世，不損汝也，何為憂色？</p><p id="pT14p0758a1513" place="inline">「第一夢：陂
<lb n="0758a16" ed="T"/>池火炎滔天者。當來比丘，善心轉少，惡逆
<lb n="0758a17" ed="T"/>熾盛，共相殺害，不可稱計。</p><p id="pT14p0758a1711" place="inline">「第二夢<note n="0758008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔者〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0758008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔者〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0758008"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>：日月
<lb n="0758a18" ed="T"/>沒，星宿亦沒。佛泥洹後，一切聲聞，隨佛泥
<lb n="0758a19" ed="T"/>洹不在世，眾生眼滅。</p><p id="pT14p0758a1909" place="inline">「第三夢：出家比丘，轉
<lb n="0758a20" ed="T"/>在於不淨坑塹之中；在家白衣，登頭出者。當
<lb n="0758a21" ed="T"/>來比丘懷毒嫉&CB00107;，至相殺害，道士斬頭，白
<lb n="0758a22" ed="T"/>衣視之，諫訶不從，死入地獄；白衣精進，死
<lb n="0758a23" ed="T"/>生天上。</p><p id="pT14p0758a2304" place="inline">「第四夢者：群&CB00337;來觝<app type="＊" source="0758004"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00247;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">突</rdg></app>栴檀林<app type="＊" source="0758005"><lem wit="【大】">怪
<lb n="0758a24" ed="T"/>之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>者。當來白衣，來入塔寺，誹謗眾僧，求其
<lb n="0758a25" ed="T"/>長短，破塔害僧。</p><p id="pT14p0758a2507" place="inline">「第五夢者：頭戴須彌山，不
<lb n="0758a26" ed="T"/>以為重者。佛泥洹後，阿難當為千阿羅漢出
<lb n="0758a27" ed="T"/>經之師，一句不忘，受悟亦多，不以為重。</p><p id="pT14p0758a2716" place="inline">「第
<lb n="0758a28" ed="T"/>六夢者：大象棄小象。將來邪見熾盛，壞我
<lb n="0758a29" ed="T"/>佛法，有德之人，皆隱不現。</p><p id="pT14p0758a2911" place="inline">「第七夢：師子死
<pb n="0758b" ed="T" id="T14.0494.0758b"/>
<lb n="0758b01" ed="T"/>者。佛泥洹後一千四百七十歲，<note n="0758009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">我＝中【三】【宮】</note><note n="0758009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">我＝中【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0758009"><lem wit="【大】">我</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">中</rdg></app>諸弟子
<lb n="0758b02" ed="T"/>修德之心，一切惡魔不得<note n="0758010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嬈＝擾【三】【宮】</note><note n="0758010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嬈＝擾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0758010"><lem wit="【大】">嬈</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">擾</rdg></app>亂；七毫者，七
<lb n="0758b03" ed="T"/>百歲後事。」</p></div1>
<lb n="0758b04" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead><note n="0758011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（佛說）＋阿【三】【宮】</note><note n="0758011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（佛說）＋阿【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0758011"><lem wit="【大】">阿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">佛說阿</rdg></app>難七夢經</jhead></juan>
</body></text></TEI.2>